<li><a href="/scp-3601">SCP-3601</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-4209">SCP-4209</a></li>
</ul>
<div style="text-align:right">
<p><sub><a href="#toc">Back to Top</a></sub></p>
</div>
</div>
<p><a name="alpha-9"></a></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone series" style="background-color: #FFFFFF;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h1 id="toc2"><span>MTF Alpha-9 (&quot;Last Hope&quot;)</span></h1>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/task-forces/alpha9alt.png"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/task-forces/alpha9alt.png/small.jpg" alt="alpha9alt.png" class="image" /></a></div>
</div>
<p><strong>Task Force Mission:</strong> The reborn Omega-7. A Mobile Task Force explicitly intended to train and utilize humanoid SCP objects in the field.</p>
<p><strong>Action Reports:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/the-seed-of-an-idea">The Seed of an Idea</a></li>
