<p><a name="beta-4"></a></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone series" style="background-color: #FFFFFF;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h1 id="toc3"><span>MTF Beta-4 (&quot;Castaways&quot;)</span></h1>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/task-forces/beta4.png"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/task-forces/beta4.png/small.jpg" alt="beta4.png" class="image" /></a></div>
</div>
<p><strong>Task Force Mission:</strong> MTF Beta-4 is a task force created with the sole purpose of assisting and monitoring GoI-466 (Wilson's Wildlife Solutions) in their interactions with local fauna-based anomalies.</p>
<p><strong>Assisting In Containment of Objects:</strong></p>
