</div>
<p><strong>Task Force Mission:</strong> Mobile Task Force Pi-1 specializes in the investigation, containment, and subsequent cleanup of anomalies in densely-populated urban environments, particularly in the New York metropolitan area.</p>
<p><strong>Assisting In Containment of Objects:</strong></p>
