<h1 id="toc38"><span>MTF Psi-8 (&quot;The Silencers&quot;)</span></h1>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/task-forces/psi8.png"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/task-forces/psi8.png/small.jpg" alt="psi8.png" class="image" /></a></div>
</div>
<p><strong>Task Force Mission:</strong> Mobile Task Force Psi-8 specializes in the investigation, tracking, containment and/or destruction of individuals suspected to be capable of or having been affected by reanimation anomalies, as well as investigating suspected cases of communication with deceased individuals. This includes the severing of devices intended to allow communication with individuals buried alive, such as bells, pipes, and phones, as well as detainment and interrogation of individuals claiming to have had contact with deceased individuals.</p>
