</div>
<p><strong>Task Force Mission:</strong> A task force composed of reality bending Foundation personnel from an alternate universe. Omega-12 is tasked with capturing <a href="/scp-3480">SCP-3480</a>-2 instances, guarding the many entities imprisoned in Area-13, and hunting down powerful uncontained reality benders elsewhere.</p>
