</div>
<p><a name="additional"></a></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone series" style="background-color: #FFFFFF;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h1 id="toc43"><span>Additional MTFs</span></h1>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p>All MTFs not meeting the requirements necessary to receive its own entry with art may be placed here. The list here should in no way be construed to be exhaustive; new MTFs are formed and disbanded all the time as the Foundation requires. If you're looking for an MTF to use, this list may be of assistance. MTFs seeing use in multiple articles may be added to this list upon request.</p>
</blockquote>
<p><a name="beta-777"></a></p>
<h2 id="toc44"><span>Beta-777 (&quot;Hecate's Spear&quot;)</span></h2>
<p><strong>Task Force Mission:</strong> Specializes in thaumaturgical ritual analysis and countermeasures; including thaumaturgical combat.</p>
<p><strong>Encounters:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-3743">SCP-3743</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-4612">SCP-4612</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-4712">SCP-4712</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-5079">SCP-5079</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-5512">SCP-5512</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-5923">SCP-5923</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-5957">SCP-5957</a></li>
</ul>
<p><a name="epsilon-7"></a></p>
<h2 id="toc45"><span>Epsilon-7 (&quot;Forget Me Nots&quot;)</span></h2>
<p><strong>Task Force Mission:</strong> Undercover task force tasked with disrupting the research and development of mnestic drugs.</p>
<p><strong>Encounters:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2111">SCP-2111</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-2358">SCP-2358</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-2438">SCP-2438</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-2828">SCP-2828</a></li>
</ul>
<p><a name="theta-5"></a></p>
<h2 id="toc46"><span>Theta-5 (&quot;The Bigger Boat&quot;)</span></h2>
<p><strong>Task Force Mission:</strong> Specialized in anomalies involving or threatening marine vehicles.</p>
<p><strong>Encounters:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2162">SCP-2162</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-1568">SCP-1568</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-1373">SCP-1373</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-1409">SCP-1409</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-3057">SCP-3057</a></li>
</ul>
<p><a name="upsilon-4"></a></p>
<h2 id="toc47"><span>Upsilon-4 (&quot;Sugar Pill&quot;)</span></h2>
<p><strong>Task Force Mission:</strong> Originally formed in order to contain <a href="/scp-2559">SCP-2559</a>, Mobile Task Force Upsilon-4 is tasked with epidemiological containment, especially with the containment of memetic outbreaks.</p>
<p><strong>Encounters:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2350">SCP-2350</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-2559">SCP-2559</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-2546">SCP-2546</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-3519">SCP-3519</a></li>
</ul>
<p><a name="phi-2"></a></p>
<h2 id="toc48"><span>Phi-2 (&quot;Clever Girls&quot;)</span></h2>
<p><strong>Task Force Mission:</strong> Task force specializing in study, tracking, capture, and hunting of prehistoric anomalies, especially dinosaurs.</p>
<p><strong>Encounters:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-3057">SCP-3057</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-3934">SCP-3934</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-3467">SCP-3467</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-4041">SCP-4041</a></li>
</ul>
<div style="text-align:right">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /></p>
<div style="text-align: left;">
<p>For a full list of Task Forces, see the <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/task-forces-complete-list">Comprehensive List of Mobile Task Forces</a>.</p>
</div>
<p><sub><a href="#toc">Back to Top</a></sub></p>
</div>
</div>

